d_b" style="height: 25px; width: 511px;" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbTechpost">教授</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_a" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>学 历：</strong></td>\r\n<td class="td_a" style="height: 25px; width: 511px;" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbEducationLevel">博士</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_b" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>所学专业：</strong></td>\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 511px;" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbMajor">计算机科学与信息安全系大数据技术研究所</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_a" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>办公电话：</strong></td>\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 511px;" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbTelOffice">85358477</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_b" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>电子邮件：</strong></td>\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 511px;" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbEmail">yangzl@nankai.edu.cn</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_a" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>研究方向：</strong></td>\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 1046px;" colspan="2" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbDirection">大数据分析与挖掘、人工智能和数据库系统</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_b" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>个人简介：</strong></td>\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 1046px;" colspan="2" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbIntroduction">分别于清华大学和日本东京大学获学士学位和博士学位。2008年7月起任东京大学生产技术研究所特任教员（历任助理教授、副教授）, 2014年4月起任南开大学教授。主要研究方向为数据分析与挖掘、人工智能和数据库系统。目前的研究兴趣是针对大数据的时序列数据分析与挖掘，短语快速检索，知识图谱建立及搜索等。天津青年千人。</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_a" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>科研项目、成果、获奖、专利等情况：</strong></td>\r\n<td class="td_a" style="height: 25px; width: 1046px;" colspan="2" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbProject">主持了日本信息推进机构资助的“基于网络隐私保护的人搜索”（2007-2008），参与了日本文部省大数据技术相关研究的两个重大项目，即“基于信息爆炸时代的新型IT 基础框架研究”(2005–2011），以及“面向超大型数据库时代的高速引擎开发和相关社会服务应用的开发和验证研究”(2010-2014)，微软亚洲研究院的“基于分类的网络查询推荐”的研究项目（2009-2010）。近年来在包括AAAI, IJCAI, ACL, WWWJ等国际学术会议杂志上发表SCI/EI论文收录30余篇。获得国际会议及研讨会 DEIM09, RRDS08,DEWS06,SEA03 最佳论文奖。担任国际学术期刊 International Journal of Social Network Mining 的编委，以及一些国际重要期刊学会如TKDE,VLDBJ,TOIS,SIGMOD,VLDB,ICDE, WWW,SIGKDD 的审稿人。</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_b" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>撰写论文、专著、教材等：</strong></td>\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 1046px;" colspan="2" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbPaper">代表性论文： <br />  <br /> [1] Yanhui Gu, Zhenglu Yang, Junsheng Zhou, Weiguang Qu, Jinmao Wei, and Xingtian Shi. A Fast Approach for Semantic Similar Short Texts Retrieval. Annual Meeting of the Association for Computational Linguistics (ACL), 2016. (CCF A) <br /> [2] Jun Wang, Jinmao Wei, and Zhenglu Yang. Supervised Feature Selection by Preserving Class Correlation. International Conference on Information and Knowledge Management (CIKM), 2016. (CCF B) <br /> [3] Jianjun Yu, Yi Shen, and Zhenglu Yang. Topic-STG: extending the session-based temporal graph approach for personalized tweet recommendation. International World Wide Web Conference (WWW), 2014. (CCF A) <br /> [4] Yanhui Gu, Zhenglu Yang, Guandong Xu, Miyuki Nakano, Masashi Toyoda, and Masaru Kitsuregawa. Exploration on efficient similar sentences extraction. WWW Journal, 17(4): 595-626, 2014. (CCF B) <br /> [5] Zhenglu Yang and Masaru Kitsuregawa. Efficient Searching Top-k Semantic Similar Words. International Joint Conference on Artificial Intelligence (IJCAI), pp. 2373-2378, 2011. (CCF A) <br /> [6] Zhenglu Yang, Jianjun Yu, and Masaru Kitsuregawa. Fast Algorithms for Top-k Approximate String Matching. AAAI Conference on Artificial Intelligence (AAAI), pp.1467-1473, 2010. (CCF A) <br /> [7] Yulan Yan, Naoaki Okazaki, Yutaka Matsuo, Zhenglu Yang, and Mitsuru Ishizuka. Unsupervised Relation Extraction by Mining Wikipedia Texts with support from Web Corpus. Annual Meeting of the Association for Computational Linguistics (ACL), pp. 1021-1029, 2009. (CCF A) <br /> [8] Zhenglu Yang, Lin Li, and Masaru Kitsuregawa. Efficient Querying Relaxed Dominant Relationship between Product Items based on Rank Aggregation. AAAI Conference on Artificial Intelligence (AAAI), pp. 1261-1266, 2008. (CCF A) <br /> [9] Lin Li, Zhenglu Yang, Ling Liu, and Masaru Kitsuregawa. Query-URL Bipartite based Approach to Personalized Query Recommendation. AAAI Conference on Artificial Intelligence (AAAI), pp. 1189-1194, 2008. (CCF A) <br /> [10 ] Zhenglu Yang, Lin Li, Botao Wang, and Masaru Kitsuregawa. Towards Efficient Dominant Relationship Exploration of the Product Items on the Web. AAAI Conference on Artificial Intelligence (AAAI), pp. 1483-1488, 2007. (CCF A) <br /> </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_a" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>讲授课程：</strong></td>\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 1046px;" colspan="2" align="left" valign="middle"> <span id="lbCourseInfo"></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="tr_b" style="height: 25px;">\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 148px;" align="center" valign="middle"><strong>社会兼职：</strong></td>\r\n<td style="height: 25px; width: 1046px;" colspan="2" align="left" valign="middle">\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p> </p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-19 08:14:58', 977, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-19 09:02:48', 977, '2016-11-19 08:14:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 2, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 11, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItem